results.description:
Job Description
RTS is a leading sports data provider. We provide live information from sports events worldwide. We have been operating in Morocco since 2009. We are looking for match reporters to cover games in Morocco for the ongoing 2024-2025 sports season.

As a match reporter, you will be required to attend games live from stadiums and send statistics through an app/phone call. 

Do you love football and the world of sports? Join our team and get paid to watch professional matches.

We pay 40 Euros per game covered in Morocco.

This is a part time job that is flexible and enjoyable with a possibility to cover several games every week. You get a bonus every 50 matches.

We are looking for reliable and serious people with good football knowledge and a good command of English.

We have openings in every city hosting Botola 1 and 2 games : Casablanca, Rabat, Marrakech, El Jadida, Tanger, Tetouan, Fes, Oujda, Berkane, Agadir, Khourigba, Safi, Soualem, Berrechid, Kenitra, Beni Mellal, Khénifra
results.competences:
Skills
The ideal candidate speaks English, has an interest in football, is comfortable going to the stadium and is reliable,
- Other sports are a real plus.
- Good command of English
- Sports Knowledge
- Punctuality
- Aware of the local sports scene.

Founded in year 2008, RTS has come a long way from its beginnings. RTS has proven itself to be the industry frontrunner in terms of innovation, foresight and vision. Our aim has been to deliver a versatile, dynamic live data service, which is second to none in terms of functionality, accuracy and reach. We focus on covering live events from different sports venues around the world, relying on a global network of more than 2,000+ highly trained match reporters who have delivered consistent results and efficiency over the years allowing us to operate in over 130+ countries worldwide. RTS covers more tournaments in more territories, than any other play-by-play service. Our backend operation is centralized in our office with more than 200+ employees who are constantly trained and evaluated to ensure the best results and product quality for our clients.
